title: Pawley's Island Bakery
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Bakery, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bakery cafe with Wi-Fi. Menu includes a veggie wrap with hummus (could order without cheese) and a veggie burger. The baked goods, however, are reported not vegan suitable. Owner understands what vegan meas and could offer catering.
